name: IAM-WHITE-03
description: v4w.enko - "IAM-WHITE-03" [Intermediate Algorithmic Multicomponent - WHITE - 03]  is the cross-pattern abstraction. Connects intermediate pattern`s instructions to demonstrate the multicomponent relationship of various geometric algorithms. Abstraction WHITE - 03 is dedicated to the "Metaball", "Voronoi diagram" and "Delaunay triangulation" transformations. Operated in diferent way. The patterns are linked to draw the algorithmic abstract artwork with each other according to the linked energy of abstract processes.  Relationship of algorithms is realized with eight charged points as main triggers which are divided in two groups and are transforming the space around. Captured as a raw data based on the custom "node-programed" software. Packed as GIF. 1024*1024px / 141 frames.
